pullRequest.title: Privatized wsoc features
pullRequest.bodyText:
Moved api bundles to their own privaate features for wsoc 1 and 1.1
Updated other features using the bundle to pull in the private feature instead

fixes #15325
Need to confirm if wsoc-1.0 private needs the WLP-Activation-Type: parallel property like wsoc-1.1

Why remove the eecompatible feature here?
